      "value": "<p><style>[data-colorid=vuir518gvv]{color:#808284} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=vuir518gvv]{color:#7b7d7f}</style><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Please see the&nbsp;</span><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542238759/\" rel=\"nofollow\">RenderMan Release Notes</a><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">&nbsp;for more details.</span></p><p>This current release offers support for:</p><ul><li><p>Blender 3.6</p></li><li><p>Blender 4.1</p></li><li><p>Blender 4.2</p></li><li><p>Blender 4.3</p></li><li><p>Blender 4.4</p></li><li><p>Blender 4.5</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"RenderManforBlenderReleaseNotes-SourceCode\">Source Code</h3><p>You can download the source code for RenderMan for Blender here: <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://github.com/prman-pixar/RenderManForBlender\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/prman-pixar/RenderManForBlender</a></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"256\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640279/inside-out-2-disgust-01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432728994&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=413\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640279/inside-out-2-disgust-01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432728994&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1024\" data-width=\"634\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640295\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"inside-out-2-disgust-01.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640279\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"3\" data-media-id=\"f4124a8b-